spec_data.Name: perl-POE-Wheel-Null
spec_data.Description:
POE::Wheel::Null creates a wheel which doesn't do anything upon put(), and
doesn't send any events to the current session.

Its function is the same as those pipes in the Enterprise's engine room
marked "GNDN".
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Fri 28 Jul 2017 02:48:29 PM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: POE Wheel that does puts data nowhere, and sends nothing
